The XD Pen offers virtual tutors a dynamic and interactive tool for annotating digital content in real-time. Its precision and sensitivity provide a natural writing experience, making it ideal for illustrating complex ideas across various subjects. Compatible with different digital platforms, the pen facilitates seamless integration into virtual classrooms, promoting collaboration and engagement.Â 

Versatile and collaborative, the XD Pen allows tutors to solve math problems, diagram scientific concepts, and provide real-time feedback on assignments. Its standout feature lies in the ability to record and save instructional sessions, creating a comprehensive archive for students to revisit at their own pace. The pen's intuitive design ensures tutors can focus on content delivery, making it an indispensable tool for enhancing the online learning experience.
